
            About Jaipur
Very popularly known as the Pink City of India, will surely make you fall in love and see everything around through pink rose coloured glasses. Jaipur is one city which has a rich royal history, many kings and queens and their multiple generations resided in lovely palaces and forts which still look as majestic and beautiful as they were and have a rich history associated with them. Not to forget the vibrant and colourful vibe of the city with respect to its handicrafts culture, the zest with which the festivals are celebrated there and of course, a very rich food culture with the Rajasthani Thali and Dal Baati dominating the whole list. The beauty of the place will surly enthral you and give you two a perfect destination for a weekend get away from nearby cities, such as Delhi.

 